As an empath, rather than
shutting down or withdrawing,

00:22:51.950 --> 00:22:54.230 align:middle line:84%
we can learn to use
this gift to serve

00:22:54.230 --> 00:22:56.405 align:middle line:84%
from a place of
compassion and empathy.

